ed="T" n="0809b12"/><persName key="A011646">釋彥偁</persName>，姓<name>龔</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000010157"><placeName>吳郡</placeName><placeName>常熟</placeName></placeName>人也。揭厲<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1031"/>戒<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>津</sic><corr>律</corr></choice>，<lb
ed="T" n="0809b13"/>錙銖<ptr type="glossary" target="#g170"/>塵務，勤求師範，唯善是從。末扣擊《繼<lb
ed="T" n="0809b14"/>宗》記<ref type="person" target="#A023367">主</ref><ptr target="#n1880"/>，得其戶牗<ptr type="glossary" target="#g906"/>，乃於<ref type="place" target="#PL000000010157">本生地</ref>講導，同好<lb
ed="T" n="0809b15"/>鳩聚，律風孔<ptr type="glossary" target="#g909"/>扇，號為<name>毘尼窟宅</name>焉。先是<placeName key="PL000000010157">海<lb
ed="T" n="0809b16"/>隅</placeName>，<persName key="A023368">巫咸氏</persName>之遺壤，<placeName key="PL000000010125">招真治</placeName><ptr target="#n1879"/>之舊墟，古寺周圍<lb
ed="T" n="0809b17"/>不全，垝垣<ptr type="glossary" target="#g914"/>而已。甞一夜有虎中獵人箭，伏<lb
ed="T" n="0809b18"/>於寺閣，哮吼不止。<persName key="A011646">偁</persName>憫之，忙係鞵，秉炬下<lb
ed="T" n="0809b19"/>閣，言欲拔之。弟子輩扶遏且止者三四，伺<lb
ed="T" n="0809b20"/>其更闌各睡，乃自持炬就拔其箭。虎耽耳<ptr type="glossary" target="#g917"/><lb
ed="T" n="0809b21"/>舐矢鏃血，顧<persName key="A011646">偁</persName>而瞑目焉。質明<ptr type="glossary" target="#g438"/>，獵師<persName key="A011647">朱德</persName>就<lb
ed="T" n="0809b22"/>寺尋虎，<persName key="A011646">偁</persName>告示其箭，<persName key="A011647">朱德</persName>悛心<ptr type="glossary" target="#g858"/>罷獵焉。<lb
ed="T" n="0809b23"/><persName key="A003552"><persName>武肅王</persName><persName>錢<roleName>氏</roleName></persName></persName>知重，每設冥齋，召行持明法<ptr type="glossary" target="#g249"/>。<lb
ed="T" n="0809b24"/>時覆肩衣自肱而墮，還自<anchor xml:id="beg0809sgsz9"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>塔</sic><corr>搭</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0809sgsz9"/>上，或見鬼物隨<lb
ed="T" n="0809b25"/>侍焉。所謂道德盛則鬼神助也。以<date from-iso="+0920-06-24" key="j20572582057286" to-iso="+0920-07-22"><name>貞明</name>六年<lb
ed="T" n="0809b26"/>六月</date>，終于山房，年九十九歲云。</p><p>次<persName key="A011648">壽<roleName><anchor xml:id="beg0809sgsz11"/>闍黎<anchor xml:id="end0809sgsz11"/></roleName></persName>者，<lb
ed="T" n="0809b27"/><placeName key="PL000000010590">淮浦</placeName>左右，貞諒<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1431"/>不群，防護正念，時少雙偶。<lb
ed="T" n="0809b28"/>傳<persName key="A001519">南山</persName>律鈔<ptr target="#n1290"/>極成，不看他面<ptr type="glossary" target="#g680"/>。<date notBefore-iso="+0835-03-10" key="j20261062052491" notAfter-iso="+0907-06-06"><name>唐</name>季</date><persName key="A007250">楊<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>奄<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1005"/><lb
ed="T" n="0809b29"/>有<placeName key="PL000000010783">廣陵</placeName>，頻召供施。四遠崇重，食<anchor xml:id="beg0809sgsz13"/>唯<anchor xml:id="end0809sgsz13"/>正命<ptr type="glossary" target="#g918"/>。不<pb ed="T" n="0809c" xml:id="T50.2061.0809c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0809c01"/>畜盈長，戶不施關。及臨壇度弟子，正<anchor xml:id="beg0809sgsz14"/>秉<anchor xml:id="end0809sgsz14"/><lb
ed="T" n="0809c02"/>羯磨<ptr type="glossary" target="#g390"/>，未周三法<ptr type="glossary" target="#g538"/>，忽爾坐亡于覆釜<ptr type="glossary" target="#g920"/>之畔，聞<lb
ed="T" n="0809c03"/>見驚歎歟！</p>
